            </p>
          </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
            <p class="para">
            The <a href="http://manpages.ubuntu.com/manpages/man8/dhclient.8.html" class="ulink" title="http://manpages.ubuntu.com/manpages/man8/dhclient.8.html">dhclient man page</a> has 
